i -> Iterator for the rows(ex: 0,1,2).
j-> Iterator for columns..resets to 0 when reaches n( ex:0,1,2 (reaches n so 0,1,2...until i reaches n) ) //Basically we compare a row with each column.
k->Iterates through the elements. If not equal breaks. Else if k==n which implies all elements were equal so we increment final ans c. then go to next column j++;
if(j reaches n) -> we go to next row and compare with all columns by reseting j to 0;

