##high level:
## 1. food needs to be separate class. In a real system, this needs to be a table. 
## 2. ranking, heap is data structure to use. for each type, we keep a heap. 
## tricky part is when rating is changed, how do we update the heap. 
## heap is not opertimized for searching an item. so for performance, we can just update it in the food class then everytime, we visit heap, check if the rating is matching with food, if not,just ignore it and delete it from heap

## other things to consider when you see this Question in an interview
